name: Owari Akane Danganronpa
description:
A LoRA of Akane Owari from Danganronpa 2. Trained on NAI.

v2 is much better and versatile. I can't think of any real use for the v1. I'm planning to updates other of my LoRAs too, but this isn't a priority (Akane was really meh so I updated her first).

You can easely switch between her short (Danganronpa 2) and long (Danganronpa 3) hair cut with the prompts "short hair" and "long hair". See samples for other good prompts.

This LoRA doesn't requires a trigger word.

Should work well with most of the anime model. Tested on AOM3 and Anythingv4.5.

I'm planning to do every Danganronpa characters. Don't hesitate to review this LoRA and tell me who you wants next!

All of my LoRAs will always be free. If you paid for this or an image using this LoRA, you got scamed! If you wants to supports me, feel free to buy me a Ko-Fi.
